---

<Layout title="Legal Notice - Music Store">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Legal Notice</h1>
    <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Representative</h2>
        <p>Taro Kimura</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Address</h2>
        <p>Disclose without delay upon request.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Phone</h2>
        <p>Disclose without delay upon request.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Email</h2>
        <p>kted@kimurataro.com</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Sales URL</h2>
        <p>https://kimurataro.gumroad.com/</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Payment Methods</h2>
        <p>Credit Card, Bank PayPal</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Additional fees and other additional charges</h2>
        <p>Communication costs when ordering / Communication costs for downloading</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Exchanges and returns (refund policy)</h2>
        <p>Please contact us via our contact form within 7 days after the point at which the order confirmation email for the downloadable product is sent out. If, 
          after investigating the situation, there is a fault due to a defect in the product itself (defect), we will take appropriate action such as re-downloading or refunding. 
          In addition, we will not be able to respond in the above manner to defects in an operating environment that differs from the operating environment recommended for the product. In the event of a refund, etc., the amount of the refund will be limited to the purchase price of the product.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Date of delivery</h2>
        <p>Immediately after ordering, you will receive an order confirmation email describing where to obtain the downloadable products.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Acceptable means of payment</h2>
        <p>Credit card, PayPal</p>
      </section>

        <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Settlement period</h2>
        <p>Credit card and Paypal payments are processed immediately.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>